# Raspberry Pi Edge (HAR Project)

## Modes
- `MODE=MOCK` – no Arduinos needed. Generates IMU-like data with `mock_stream.py`.
- `MODE=BLE`  – connects to two Nano 33 IoT devices (wrist + ankle). Fill UUIDs/names in `ble_receiver.py`.

## Setup
```bash
python -m venv .venv
source .venv/bin/activate
pip install -r requirements.txt
